properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters east of Ipswich Bay and the Stellwagen Bank National Marine Sanctuary
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 7 at 6:56PM EST until February 8 at 5:00AM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 kt with gusts up to 45 kt and seas
7 to 12 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal waters east of Ipswich Bay and the Stellwagen
Bank National Marine Sanctuary.

* WHEN...Until 5 AM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 AM EST SATURDAY... ...STORM WARNING IS CANCELLED
